captions.text: Don't do it! I'm sorry, I blew it.

I'll leave you, and this
whole cruel world behind
Please, don't throw it all away!

I swear I'll never leave,
I'll never stray!

I promise I'll never leave
you for another!

And I'm sorry that
I shot your brother.

Please take me back
I swear I'll make this work!

You always say things like that, 
and then you treat me like a jerk.

When it comes to love
you come first.

It's too late, you'll never change
you're the worst!

I can change, I can learn
new positions!

If I die, you'll know the
pain I feel inside!

You'll suffer the way
I did when you ied.

Sorry, I thought with...
the hair...
